					(thickness 0.15)
				)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "ESP32-WROVER-E and ESP32-WROVER-IE are two powerful, generic WiFi-BT-BLE MCU modules that target a wide variety of applications, ranging from low-power sensor networks to the most demanding tasks, such as voice encoding, music streaming and MP3 decoding. ESP32-WROVER-E comes with a PCB antenna, and ESP32-WROVER-IE with an IPEX antenna. They both featurea 4 MB external SPI flash and an additional 8 MB SPI Pseudo static RAM (PSRAM)."
